   GLB_NOLIBGTL -- could not open gtlayout library
   GLB_NOLIBINT -- could not open intuition library
   GLB_NOWINDOW -- could not open window
   GLB_NOMEM -- out of memory

EXAMPLE
@{fg shine}@{fg text}
